frames.caption: A warrior in ornate armor kneels on a battlefield, surrounded by soldiers holding spears. Dark storm clouds loom overhead, with a bolt of lightning illuminating the scene.
frames.description: The scene depicts a dramatic moment on a battlefield, where a warrior kneels amidst a group of soldiers. The atmosphere is tense, with stormy skies and lightning adding to the intensity.

frames.caption: A warrior kneels before a leader in ornate armor amidst a vast army under a stormy sky. Lightning strikes in the background, adding drama to the tense scene. The soldiers stand in formation, holding spears, as they witness the moment.
frames.description: The scene depicts a dramatic and intense moment on a battlefield, where a kneeling warrior faces a leader in front of an assembled army. The dark, stormy sky and lightning enhance the epic and solemn atmosphere.
